title: Rare Meat
description:
A fan's compilation (credit: nathang78) of rare Meat Puppets tracks: promos, B-sides, EP's etc., from ca. 1991-2000.  Derrick Bostrum, original Pups drummer, posted a link to this on his site, but the link died, so here it is.  Be sure to seed and keep these prime cuts fresh for all to savor!

Read more at Bostrum's site: <a href="
http://derrickbostrom.com/rare-meat-a-fans-compilation/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://derrickbostrom.com/rare-meat-a-fans-compilation/</a>
